        h4
          b  The cloud worker is enabled to provide edge level handling of traffic across all HTTP requests and responses made, and in case of certain conditions, redirect appropriate requests/generate responses from the edge.
        p With the implementation of multiple asynce functions with eventlisteners to await for curl requests made by certain user agents and handle the traffic redirection.
        p When a user makes a curl command to parse the website, the cloud worker ensures a redirect is made unless params for no-redirect are requested.
        p Custom headers are appended to all requests made across the site for tracking purposes. 
        br
        
        b  You can view the custom tracking headers in the section of request headers above.
        h4
        b  Request Header From Cloud Worker:
